# Installation Guide

## Requirements
- Node.js 18 or newer
- npm (recommended) or yarn

## Steps
```bash
git clone https://github.com/mydsrt-artweb/dsrt-app.git
cd dsrt-app
npm install
npm run dev

Environment Variables

Copy .env.example to .env.local and configure values:

NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:3000/api

---

